sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Config UI
    participant GitLab
    participant App as Spring Boot Webhook API
    participant DB as App DB
    participant DevOps as DevOps Deployment API
    participant K8s as Kubernetes Cluster

    User->>UI: Edit env config
    UI->>GitLab: Create branch + commit + Merge Request
    GitLab-->>UI: MR id / URL
    UI->>DB: Store MR tracking record

    actor Reviewer
    Reviewer->>GitLab: Approve + merge MR

    GitLab->>App: POST /webhooks/gitlab<br/>Merge Request Event
    App->>App: Validate GitLab token/signature
    App->>App: Check event type = merge_request
    App->>App: Check object_attributes.state = merged

    App->>GitLab: Optional: Fetch MR details
    GitLab-->>App: MR metadata

    App->>DB: Mark config change as MERGED
    App->>DevOps: POST /deploy-config<br/>env, app, repo, commitSha
    DevOps->>K8s: Checkout env config + copy to resource config folder
    DevOps-->>App: Deployment accepted/result
    App->>DB: Store deployment status
    App-->>GitLab: 200 OK